Package org.apache.wiki.api.spi

JSPWiki's SPI package. This package holds all the service provider interfaces provided by JSPWiki to obtain instances of objects from the org.apache.wiki.api.core package.

Package Specification

Related Documentation

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    AclsSPI
    SPI used to locate and provide Acl and AclEntry instances.
    ContentsSPI
    SPI used to locate and provide Page and Attachment instances.
    ContextSPI
    SPI used to locate and provide Context instances.
    EngineSPI
    SPI used to locate and provide Engine instances.
    SessionSPI
    SPI used to locate and provide Session instances.
